                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"/></a></p></div><div class="sources"><h3>Events</h3><p class="indent"> The heresy of Adelphius had been condemned by Soteric of Caesarea and the bishops of
                                Cappadocia, the bishops of
                                Pontus, and the bishops of
                                Galatia.  <a href="/3038-40" class="factoid-more">See factoid page
